  "body": "Using factory will make hardhat's error stack become such as following,  18695 lines of errors, hardhat just simply print the source code no matter what...\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/33961674/209090835-9070fbc4-0cc2-488d-865d-07fee634c72a.png)\r\n\r\nthis error seems was reported [long time ago](https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/issues/2848) and hardhat is still not wiling to take it serious. It's not really usable at the moment, people always need to set gasLimit to see the real errors\r\n\r\nAnyway to just turn off the gas estimation? it's not really useful in test environment unless people really want.",
